0114g text BUTTON 1
0126y text BUTTON 2
0138l text BUTTON 3
0150r text MOVEMENT ARROWS
1503w text move way up (north) or down (south) from the battlefield
1560y text to end your turn
1704w text move left (home player) or right (away player)
1751y text to see the cards on hand
1905w text press ENTER at the main screen
1937y text to browse all currently defined cards
2105r text           press ESCAPE repeatedly to exit the program
2205v text          any of function keys with code 27 will do that
2305x text           including regular arrow keys unfortunatelly
